Requirements
------------

The IP/ROHC program uses the following external dependencies:

 +-----------+---------------+--------------------------------+
 | Name      | License       | Website                        |
 +-----------+---------------+--------------------------------+
 | libyaml   | MIT license   | http://pyyaml.org/wiki/LibYAML |
 +-----------+---------------+--------------------------------+
 | ROHC      | GPL2+         | http://rohc-lib.org/           |
 +-----------+---------------+--------------------------------+
 | GnuTLS    | LGPLv3+       | http://www.gnutls.org/         |
 +-----------+---------------+--------------------------------+

Cmake (http://www.cmake.org/) is used for configuring and building the program.

Please install Cmake and any above dependencies from sources or with your
favorite package manager before going further.


Build and install
-----------------

Configure the program:

 $ cmake CMakeLists.txt

Build the program:

 $ make all

Install the program:

 $ make install

